Package: radsafer
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Radiation Safety
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mark Hogue <mark.hogue@srs.gov>
Maintainer: Mark Hogue <mark.hogue@srs.gov>
Description: Functions are provided that are useful for health 
  physics and radiological engineering. This is far from a complete 
  set. If you have additional functions to include, please email 
  the author. Functions include source decay (including Cf-252 
  sources), analog meter simulation, disk to disk solid angle, and
  utilities to make MCNP model building simpler. *
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: testthat, tidyverse
Imports: ggplot2
URL: https://github.com/markhogue/radsafer
BugReports: https://github.com/markhogue/radsafer/issues
